      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COLLINDA POPS (2) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 5th (24.49) at Bendigo. Has ability and looks hard to stop. INVICTUS HARMONY (1) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (17.27) at Healesville over 300m. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from seven starts. Expecting another good run. ROSE OPAL (7) showed good early burn but run over late to finish 5th at Sale in Grade 5 company. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Can do much better this time. PAW CHEYENNE (3) can add to a sequence of top-three finishes.",
